### ğŸ”„ API Routes (CRUD)
| Route | Method | Description |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| `/api/tweets` | GET | List all tweets |
| `/api/tweets` | POST | Add new tweet (username + tweet) |
| `/api/tweets/:id` | PUT | Update tweet text |
| `/api/tweets/:id` | DELETE | Delete tweet by ID |

### ğŸ›¡ Middleware
- **App-level:** Logs each request as `METHOD + URL + Time`  
  Example: `POST /api/tweets  10:45:22 AM`
- **Route-level (POST/PUT):**  
  - Validate tweet not empty  
  - Minimum length = 5 characters  

